title: Should we grant Jack 100NXM for designing a new wNXM interface?
body:
Jack has created a new wNXM interface to help users wrap and unwrap their NXM. The UI is clearer and it means that, while MCR% is <100%, users can still trade their NXM if they want. 

https://nexus-wrapper.netlify.app/
author: 0x7Cf6D8a0940344a51E797F5C1e5b654deEEf7C00
